1978;;Maraschino Cherry;;American;;Radley Metzger;;Gloria Leonard, Annette Haven, Constance Money;;adult film;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maraschino_Cherry_(1978_film);;Maraschino Cherry, the owner of a high-class escort service in New York City, teaches her younger sister about the business.[3][4] The two sisters reflect on a series of erotic episodes related to the service and its clients.[4]